column1: # Table S1. ALG-3/4 26G-RNA targets and mRNA-Seq expression. Related to Figure 2.
# List of 1408 ALG-3/4 26G-RNA target genes and their expression by mRNA-Seq (RPM) in WT and alg-3/4 males grown at 25°C.
# WT RPM = WT male 25°C mRNA-Seq RPM normalized to the total number of genome-matching reads
# alg-3/4 RPM = alg-3/4 male 25°C mRNA-Seq RPM normalized to the total number of genome-matching reads
# Ratio = Expression of alg-3/4 relative to WT (alg-3/4 RPM)/ (alg-3/4 RPM + WT RPM)
